===Noun===
'''marriage'''
#The socially and/or legally sanctioned [[union]] that usually forms the nucleus of a [[family]] and is generally considered to be between one man and one woman, i.e., [[husband]] and [[wife]].
#In some societies, a [[union]] of a man and multiple women ([[polygamy]]), or a woman and multiple men ([[polyandry]])
#In some societies, a same-sex union between two women or two men.
#A [[join]]ing of two [[part]]s

